### 0. 서버 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/api/hello

### 1. 커뮤니티 게시글 작성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts
USER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "첫 커뮤니티 글",
  "content": "커뮤니티 테스트입니다."
}

### 2. 커뮤니티 게시글 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts

### 3. 커뮤니티 게시글 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1

### 4. 커뮤니티 게시글 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1
USER-ID: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수정된 커뮤니티 글",
  "content": "수정된 내용입니다."
}

### 5. 수정 결과 다시 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1

### 6. 댓글 작성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/community/comments
USER-ID: 2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "첫 댓글입니다."
}

### 7. 댓글 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1/comments

### 8. 좋아요 추가
POST http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1/like
USER-ID: 2

### 9. 좋아요 취소
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1/like
USER-ID: 2

### 10. 게시글 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/community/posts/1
USER-ID: 1